Syntax: palmstrike <target>

Delivers a powerful open-hand palm strike. Palmstrike is a Pugilist-line
unarmed attack skill that uses the heel of the palm for maximum impact.
It is handled by the Pugilist attack system alongside aurabolt and other
unarmed techniques.

Palmstrike is available to Pugilist-class characters and their remort
descendants (Monk, Brawler, and the Martial Artist adept class).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp palmstrike aurabolt punch pummel spinfist
